Event Update Notification

Hello <%= @customer.name || @customer.email %>,

We're writing to inform you that an event you've booked tickets for has been updated:

Event Details:
- Event: <%= @event.title %>
- Date: <%= @event.date.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %>
- Venue: <%= @event.venue %>
- Your Ticket: <%= @ticket.ticket_type %>
- Quantity: <%= @booking.quantity %>

Changes Made:
<% @changes.each do |field, value| %>
- <%= field.capitalize %>: <%= value[1] %> (was: <%= value[0] %>)
<% end %>

If you have any questions regarding these changes, please contact us.
Thank you for your understanding!